Package: leman2000
Type: Package
Title: Tonal Contextuality Model of Leman (2000)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peter M. C. Harrison
Maintainer: Peter M. C. Harrison <pmch2@cam.ac.ukt>
Description: This package allows you to run the tonal contextuality model of Leman (2000) on arbitrary audio files. Under the hood it uses a Dockerised version of the IPEM Toolbox.
